headtouch: Headpats, headpatty pat, patty patty head, heady heady pat pat~ Ahahah!
battle: I don't want to do this... but you leave me no choice!
mission_complete: Bingo, this looks great. Commander, we've received stellar rewards!
touch2: Hahah, I know how much you enjoy doing lewd things like this.

home: Welcome back. As much as I want you to be successful, I'm just as happy with everything staying the way it is.
main: Too much work to process? We all know what a tough job it is to command a fleet. So please, let me give you some assistance.|We are who we are now thanks to you, Commander. And while not everyone respects you, they are grateful for what you do. You really should be proud of yourself for that. I-I feel more for you than just respect, though!|I don't mind fading into the background when I'm with my friends, but when I'm with you, I want everyone to see it. Heheh, in a friendly way, of course.|Once the war has ended, then we can discuss everything we'll do once the war ends. For now, we must focus all our efforts on fighting to eventually achieve peace.
login: Don't be afraid to ask for my help if you need it. It is, after all, a secretary's job to support her Commander.
detail: I've said it time and time again: I'm not fit to be the joint exercise flagship or for any other prominent position! Why won't they listen when I say I'd screw it up horribly?! ...C-Commander?! Oh, ahh...

mission_complete: Report: working as an idol has improved my capabilities. Nice!
touch: I'm practicing at the moment... Do you need something, Master?
touch2: Comet told me that people shouldn't readily get to touch idols... Master, does this qualify as sexual harassment?
home: Master, I just finished a lesson, and... was wondering if we could enjoy a little chat?
feeling5: I completely understand what it means to be an idol now. It's about using my abilities to their fullest to sing brilliant, emotionally touching songs to the world. "Thank you," Master.
mission: Between a photoshoot, performance, or radio show, which should I focus on today, Master?
main: Concept in memory detailed as "saving the world by singing" detected. Is such a thing possible, even for me, Master?|Emotion-packed singing was assessed to be effective at touching Master's heart... Master, won't you... listen to my song?|Promotional materials' claim of me being "inexpressive" are... likely not accurate. I am like everyone else; I want to sing with a bright smile.

mail: Master, I'd like your opinion on my participation in this contest...
login: To do: vocals, dancing, and band aesthetics. Master, what I should I focus on today...?
detail: Information request: Master, how do you like my singing?

feeling5: I-I wasn't expecting you to actually carry me around the port... I'm stunned... Listen, I don't mind being with you, but stop treating me like baby!

detail: I'm so glad we finally can be together, Ariake! All that time I spent worrying about when I'd be able to see you seems like a distant illusion now…

touch: Hehe, I think I want to touch you too, Commander.
touch2: Hehe, I'll join you in a minute, okay?
login: Welcome, Commander. Time for another day of hard work. By the way... Have you been wearing your bridle like we talked about?
win_mvp: Hehehe, I'm happy if you are.
feeling5: Still feeling a little uneasy? Just wait a bit longer. You need to stay bound to me like this for now, but sooner or later you won't have to think anymore, you won't have to worry, and you can forget all that pain.
detail: Commander, are you hungry? Well, you'll just have to wait. Once I say 'okay,' then you can eat.
home: You did so well on that sortie... Now you just let me take care of everything.
main: Commander, what's wrong? I'm here, and I'm not going anywhere.|It's a big responsibility to have someone trust you so much. But don't worry, I'm holding your reins tightly.|Just let me know when you'd like to talk to another girl. You'd be very embarrassed to be seen like this, hm? touch: Comrade Commander, today's handshake. Mmm. Let us properly follow proper protocols today.
touch2: Is this what the Iris would call a "breach of etiquette?"
detail: This port has such abundance. That leaves me one core duty. I must bring emotional enrichment to your life.
home: Comrade Commander, please eat this. Think nothing of it. Call it a personal supplement.
main: I need only focus my attentions on battle? That is a reasonable decision... But does it mean my clerical skills did not pass muster?|nil|nil

touch2: You love it when they're big, don'tcha? And I love you

detail: You wanna know more about the war I fought so hard in, darling? Heheh! Maybe I should brief you then~ Not that I have to, someone else can tell you of my exploits.
login: So, what are we starting the day with, darling? ♪
main: Secretary work, huh... I'll do it if you can beat me at a game. Although you have any chance of winning anyway♪|Mh...! I think I just strained my back... N-no, I didn't say anything!|nil

touch: I see, I see, so you want to fully grasp the extent of my rigging. Very well! I have no objections, for your courage is commendable as well!
touch2: You are forgiven, comrade! Such courage deserves to be rewarded! Come, put your hands all over me until you've had your fill!
main: Comrade~ have a bit more to drink~ That Marat can't keep up with me~ C'mon, keep me company until dawn.|nil|No strong enemies around? I feel your frustration, comrade... Well then, come at me. Let's make life worth living!

mail: Attention: confirmation required for new mail. A-ahem!

touch: Your gaze makes me feel odd, Master...
